# Static headers for docs.aggregator.gg.
# Search-engine preview-URL blocking is configured at the CF Pages level
# (Settings → Branch deploys → Production: docs.aggregator.gg only; preview
# branches get auto-generated *.aggregator-docs.pages.dev URLs which are
# excluded from sitemap and emit X-Robots-Tag: noindex via the build).
# See ADR-027 Decision 8 / Resolved Decision 5 for rationale.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
